{"tid":949864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食環署研究分開屠宰香港豬及中國豬","createTime":"2018-12-21T06:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T18:36:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6b58f82f01927e5ca1b7b98032e7cab7143ee7ec","tid":949864,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】內地非洲豬瘟疫情擴散，食環署正與業界商討把本地和內地供港豬隻分開到不同屠房屠宰，一旦發現病豬會銷毀有關豬隻。不過專家認為，應該把屠場其他健康豬隻都銷毀。<br />\n<br />\n現時上水屠房和荃灣屠房會同時屠宰本地豬和內地供港豬隻，食物安全專員何玉賢表示，因應內地非洲豬瘟疫情，正與業界商討把本地和內地豬分流到不同屠房。<br />\n<br />\n現時屠房若發現豬隻受感染，食安中心人員只會銷毀病豬，其他豬隻會照樣推出市場。何玉賢指出，豬隻於屠房停留時間短，相信感染其他豬風險不大。不過有專家認為，有機會令已感染但未發病的豬流出市面。<br />\n<br />\n王啟熙亦指出，需要提防本地野豬受感染，以免病毒經本地野豬擴散。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=331510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331510&d=7ffFDP7bgnrbKwdqLOmdTTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=58b16954\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331510&h=3c755c4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=331510</a>"},{"pid":"1def7240f110968362b984c494648fa34140c701","tid":949864,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e79bdc44cf86faafbc701cd6f2c5aac2b9d0be47","tid":949864,"uid":119875,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"食環搞港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a7dc5a8fb3a6132239d829c6674a8ba267da43","tid":949864,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7274bdffc2c2e9d022a6340bbeb326c25155d86","tid":949864,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:07:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c92345a614a176c3a68fb440641479bf6ae1653c","tid":949864,"uid